<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('navbar') %>

    <div class="container-fluid blanco">
      <br />
      <div class="row encabezado">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-4 login">
          <form
            action="/designer/login"
            method="post"
            enctype="application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
          >
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="exampleFormControlInput1" class="form-label"
                >Email</label
              >
              <input
                type="email"
                class="form-control"
                id="exampleFormControlInput1"
                placeholder="name@example.com"
                name="email"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3 row">
              <label for="inputPassword" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label"
                >Password</label
              >
              <br />
              <br />
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <input
                  type="password"
                  class="form-control"
                  id="inputPassword"
                  name="password"
                />
              </div>
            </div>

            <button class="btn boton6" type="submit">Acceder</button>
          </form>
          <br />
          <img
            src="https://comprarcamisetas.es/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/bar-vader-camijetas-web-hombre_-300x300.png"
            style="width: 80%"
            alt=""
          />
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-8 postlogin">
          <h3><a class="blanco" href="/">ARRECIFE STYLE</a></h3>
          <br />
          <img
            src="https://e00-expansion.uecdn.es/assets/multimedia/imagenes/2022/01/07/16415599974751.jpg"
            alt=""
            style="width: 75%"
          />
          <br />

          <p>
            Inicia sessión en la web y accede a tu perfil, para agregar tus
            nuevos diseños o editar cambias en tú colección.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p>
            Si aún no te has registrado y quieres formar parte de la familia de
            ARRECIFE STYLE, pasate por la página de registro y

            <a class="btn boton2" href="/designer/register">Registrate</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="bg-dark text-center text-white">
      <div class="container p-4 pb-0">
        <section class="foot mb-4">
          <a class="btn-floating m-1" href="#" role="button"
            ><img
              src="/images/iconos/facebook.png"
              style="width: 5vh"
              alt="" /><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i
          ></a>

          <!-- Twitter -->
          <a class="btn-floating m-1" href="#!" role="button"
            ><img src="/images/iconos/gorjeo.png" style="width: 5vh" alt="" /><i
              class="fab fa-twitter"
            ></i
          ></a>

          <!-- Google -->
          <a class="btn-floating m-1" href="#!" role="button">
            <img src="/images/iconos/instagram.png" style="width: 5vh" alt="" />
            <i class="fab fa-google"></i
          ></a>

          <!-- Instagram -->
          <a class="btn-floating m-1" href="#!" role="button">
            <img src="/images/iconos/whatsapp.png" style="width: 5vh" alt="" />
            <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i
          ></a>
        </section>
        <!-- Section: Social media -->
      </div>
      <!-- Grid container -->

      <div class="text-center p-3" style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)">
        © 2022 Copyright:
        <a class="text-white" href="https://mdbootstrap.com/"
          >arrecifistyle.es</a
        >
      </div>
    </footer>

    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
